aditional Chinese culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3450370/extras/2f32b20aca32e615078457d233ff681f.poster.avif?t=1761531276\" width=452 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3450370/extras/2f32b20aca32e615078457d233ff681f.webm?t=1761531276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3450370/extras/2f32b20aca32e615078457d233ff681f.mp4?t=1761531276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The developer states:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hello everyone UU who love the street series, it is a pleasure to meet you with our new \"Street Li Fang Biography\", and the game is planned to be launched during the Spring Festival next year. As a derivative of the \"Street\" story, \"Street Li Fang Biography\" from the perspective of Duan Li Fang to complete the story, if you have not experienced the \"Street\" UU can also complete the experience to play \"Street\", of course, you can also directly experience the work is no problem. Hope this game can give you UU a complete, quality game experience ~ Thank you again for your street friends have been the support and love, we \"street Fang\" goodbye ~~</p>",
